blog.description:
" Elle voulait une vie d'aventures, une vie folle, une vie plus grande qu'elle.Et l'on disait tout autour d'elle : [Ygraïn] rêve". Timothée de Fombelle, Victoria rêve

Je ne sais pas dessiner, les artworks que vous verrez ici ne sont pas les miens. Mais vous trouverez toujours un lien vers une gallerie de leurs auteurs. Personnellement, je ne fais que des montages (wallpaper, digiscrap, bannière ...) à partir de captures d'écran (screencap).. Ce tumblr est ma gallerie de rêves éphémères, mon échappée belle où je viens me ressourcer, me changer les idées, trouver un support à mes rêveries grâce aux fabuleux arts de d'autres artistes. .
Pour me contacter, en cas de problème: ygrain@gmail.com

Sinon: mon blog de lecture est: https://les-lectures-d-ygrain.tumblr.com/

summary: Doc, do you know how much wood would a woodchuck chuck if a woodchuck could chuck wood?
question: Doc, do you know how much wood would a woodchuck chuck if a woodchuck could chuck wood?
answer: “I’m a time traveler, I have watched the first woodchuck who could chuck wood chuck wood. Yes, I know how much wood a woodchuck would chuck if a woodchuck could chuck wood. Give it a couple years, they’re like beavers. Ravenous. Mind the teeth.”

summary: left: ellie’s first briefing right: ellie’s briefing, end of season the way they’ve used camera framing to showcase ellie’s...
caption:
left: ellie’s first briefing
right: ellie’s briefing, end of season

the way they’ve used camera framing to showcase ellie’s growth as a leader and a detective is fantastic. the space ellie takes up in the frame, where she stands in the composition of the shot, her size and location relative to other officers – it all works to highlight the change in her demeanor and confidence. standouts: (1) that shot of ellie nervous by herself vs. ellie as the lead amongst her team; (2) that behind shot of her sidelined, with her team taking up most of the frame/looking intimidating, vs. her situated in the center of the screen, with other officers minimized, emphasizing her status as superior officer. just brilliant work.
